{"tid":2024331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"１５歲手足燒柴灣狗宿　認罪候判　被捕時口鼻流血","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T14:34:16.000Z","uid":90282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"caba014b5c31629a54c22eff9af6ad7aec1b2550","tid":2024331,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:12:59.000Z","msg":"去年 11 月 18 日，大批示威者被困理工大學期間，有人呼籲 18 區「開花、燒狗屋」救理大，期間一名 15 歲少年涉於柴灣已婚警察宿舍外掟汽油彈縱火，當場被捕，少年其後被控縱火罪，他今於東區裁判法院少年法庭認罪，獲裁判官何俊堯批准繼續保釋至 7 月 14 日判刑。控方確認事件中無人受傷，維修費約 250 元，裁判官則指「相信唯一受傷嘅可能係被告，係被制服嘅時候」，據悉，被告被制服後曾癱坐地上，口鼻流血，褲上亦有數處血跡。<br />\n<br />\n被告於獲悉可獲保釋後鬆了一口氣，多名到庭旁聽的親友亦低頭拭淚，被告父親於離庭時更緊捉被告手臂，眼泛淚光，狀甚激動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告生長於單親家庭，家人於他幼稚園時已發現他有異常，直至他約 7 歲時確診自閉症。辯方又呈上親友及師長撰寫的求情信，指他本性純良，但因自閉症對事件的判斷力較差，如獲得協助，相信重犯機會非常低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/15%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%8E%9F%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%99%82%E5%8F%A3%E9%BC%BB%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F15%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259F%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E6%258E%259F%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%25BC%25BB%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%2580%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7msgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=3d85a301\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F15%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259F%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E6%258E%259F%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%25BC%25BB%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%2580%2F&h=4af8e1a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/15%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%8E%9F%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%99%82%E5%8F%A3%E9%BC%BB%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80/</a>"},{"pid":"2d4efe01c254f768f794ceb76f66165a8aa69eb5","tid":2024331,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"好好珍惜呢兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46a696a25aff4dcc73be249ddca01143d9e144d","tid":2024331,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:19:53.000Z","msg":"之前搜到火魔都判一年，呢單斷正都唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0ad15e0641fdbabbb9f4209cb400cb18bc5aab","tid":2024331,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"個女仔"}]}